\\
\begin{align}
f(x) \approx f(x_0) +f&amp;rsquo;(x_0)(x-x_0) \\
x_{n+1} = x_n  - \frac{f(x_n)}{f&amp;rsquo;(x_n)}，n = 0,1,2,&amp;hellip;
\end{align}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
